version_description:
Want to show off your skills on the pitch like never before? Update now to check out our all-new, bite-sized Skill Games feature. 

Here’s how it works:

Choose your daily challenge – from shooting, ground passing, and dribbling, to crossing, penalties, and more. Then, pick the right player for each challenge and get in there! Beat the challenge to earn rewards!
Thanks for playing FIFA 16 Ultimate Team!
Hey footballers! We’ve made a few off-the-pitch enhancements to improve your gameplay experience. Thanks for playing FIFA 16 Ultimate Team.
